{"text":"The Composable Architecture (TCA, for short) is a library for building applications in a consistent","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and understandable way, with composition, testing, and ergonomics in mind. It can be used in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"SwiftUI, UIKit, and more, and on any Apple platform (iOS, macOS, tvOS, and watchOS).","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/composablearchitecture"}}}